n 400 newspapermen that the address he was mak fng to them was the only ex eeption which I have made in my plans for a private and y personal visit to this great and powerful nation The Catholic Church and the Holy Father Pope Pius XI desire greatly the pro teetion of the peacesocial peace and peace among the 5 nations the then Cardinal Pacelli told the gathering He also told the newsmen that His Holiness appeals to you who have great responsibil ity in reporting facts and in inspiring public opinion to labor for the salvation of humanity and to elevate it to ward its greatest its highest destiny up job You will never see Christ or Christians in Sacred Scripture approving birth con trol Mahatma Gandhig comment on this practice as"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-09-04T23:14:09.778Z", "group": ["ndnp/ohi", "ohio-historical-society-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83007243/1958-05-02/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_amaryllis_ver01:data:sn83007243:00414210247:1958050201:0514/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=303&w=202", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_amaryllis_ver01:data:sn83007243:00414210247:1958050201:0514/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=607&w=404", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ohi/batch_ohi_amaryllis_ver01/data/sn83007243/00414210247/1958050201/0514.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["columbus", "ohio", "united states", "franklin"], "location_city": ["columbus"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["franklin"], "location_state": ["ohio"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["0", "0000000004", "4", "7", "2", "1", "sn83007243"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn83007243"], "number_page": ["0000000004"]